Telkom has received a new number range for its mobile service. Telkom has sent a mail to its business partners detailing the new number range, which forms part of the “067” group. The new sub-range of the 067 segment is 800 0000 to 999 9999. This is 2,000,000 numbers. To see which number ranges are operated by which mobile providers, take a look at our article on the matter. Telkom operates the 0670-0672 range for its mobile service in South Africa.